Class XMLParse

    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • softwareproject.XMLParse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler

    public class XMLParse
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
    This class extends the DefaultHandler class. It reads in an XML document to be used by an application.

        public void readXML(java.lang.String file)
        Reads in the XML file and parses it into the application. If the XML file does not exist, it throws an IOException, SAXException, or ParserConfigurationException.
